Text: This movie is not even out on Blu-Ray yet, and the aspect ratio of this file is 1.85:1, not the 2.40:1 ratio the movie was originally shown in. This leads me to believe that it's an HDTV rip, which is fine, and looks good for what it is, but I've seen better rips from actual Blu-Ray discs.
